	Upgrade to FDL 1.3, keep COPYING in repository.
	* Makefile.am (MAINTAINERCLEANFILES): Don't remove COPYING.
	* .cvsignore: Don't ignore it.
	* .gitignore: Likewise.
	* COPYING: Store in repository, per automake 1.10.2
	recommendation.
