2008-05-22  Eric Blake  <ebb9@byu.net>

	Don't allow failure to freeze give exit status of 0.
	* src/freeze.c (produce_frozen_state): Guarantee non-zero exit on
	fopen failure.
	* doc/m4.texinfo (Using frozen files): Test the fix.
