	(usage): Now done by closeout module.
	* src/builtin.c (m4_m4exit): Likewise.
	(m4_undivert, include): Adjust callers.
	* src/freeze.c (reload_frozen_state): Likewise.
	* src/path.c (m4_path_search): Rename from path_search.
