	* src/builtin.c (WEXITSTATUS): Provide fallback definition.
	(m4_esyscmd): Set sysval to 0xffff, to accomodate both
	big-endian and little-endian wait status definitions.
	(m4_sysval): Use WEXITSTATUS.
